_:N289c89dd141b4707951a78a567b4cd39 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Alex Davies-Jones was Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Ministry of Justice from 9 July 2024 to 12 May 2026. She was elected as the MP for Pontypridd in July 2019.</p>\n" .
